claim.claim-text:
A lighting device (100) comprising:
a substrate (150) on which light emitting elements (151) are mounted;
a reflector (120) configured to reflect light emitted from the light emitting elements (151) and separated from the substrate by an insulator;
a housing (110) having an installation surface (110a) on which the substrate (150) is provided; and
a support unit (112) that extends from the installation surface (110a) to support the reflector (120).
